        <writer lang="cpp"><![CDATA[<span style="font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 10pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: windowtext; background-color: Transparent; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt; line-height: 115%">
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">Obs.: O momento atuante pode ser alterado na aba de C&#193;LCULO DOS ESFOR&#199;OS </span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">SOLICITANTES. </span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify; font-size: 9pt; color: Red">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">Caso necessite refinar mais ainda os c&#225;lculos para Combina&#231;&#227;o Quase </span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">Permanente (CQP), recalcule as cargas distribu&#237;das de entrada por meio </span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">da formula&#231;&#227;o: q(entrada) =  gk + Σ (Ψ2 * qjk).</span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify; font-size: 9pt; color: Red">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="color: Red">Aplicando o respectivo fator de redu&#231;&#227;o das cargas acidentais.</span></span></div></span>]]></writer>
